       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. UNSOLIC1.
      * UNSOLICITED CARD - REVERSE CHARGES + 2X PENALTY
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-CHARGES-BILLED         PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-REVERSAL               PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-PENALTY                PIC 9(9)V99 VALUE ZERO.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-CHARGES-BILLED
           PERFORM 2000-REMEDY
           DISPLAY 'PEN: ' WS-PENALTY
           STOP RUN.
       2000-REMEDY.
           MOVE WS-CHARGES-BILLED TO WS-REVERSAL
           COMPUTE WS-PENALTY = 2 * WS-REVERSAL.
